{"title":"漓江抒情","authors":["许幸之"],"dates":[{"year":1983,"month":2,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"漓江抒情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"许幸之"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"静静江边古渡头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"螺丝山下水悠悠；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牧童牛背吹短笛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"少女农闲学渡舟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"群山如笋密如林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竹影婆娑水更清；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欸乃渔舟网未落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平湖野鹜袅飞鸣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漓江渔火似星河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水上金蛇逐浪波；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"待命渔鹰潜水出，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盘餐兼味不需多。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}